original_title: Manhattan: Lafayette Street - Great Jones Street
text:
(1)

380, 382, and 384-388 (only part of which is shown) Lafayette Street (running from left to right in centre of view), west side, from Great Jones Street (left, running from fore to background), to but not including East 4th Street. Also shown is Great Jones Street, north side, west from Lafayette to Broadway. The gasoline station is at the N.E. corner of Great Jones Street.

March 16, 1934.

P. L. Sperr.

(2)

The same, showing a complete view of No. 384-388, a 12-story building at the S.W. corner of East 4th Street.

March 16, 1934.

P. L. Sperr.
